<taxonomicName authority="Benjamin, 2017" authorityName="Benjamin" authorityYear="2017" class="Arachnida" family="Thomisidae" genus="Epidius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="13" pageNumber="481" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mahavira" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="481">Epidius mahavira</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[274,366,212,236]" pageId="13" pageNumber="481" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, appear to occur in the same two localities. This might be due to mislabeling.
</paragraph>
